          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Rural Hospital Extensions for Low-volume Programs Act of 2022 or the Rural HELP Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill makes certain payment adjustments for Medicare-dependent hospitals and low-volume hospitals permanent (the adjustments currently expire at the end of FY2022).</p>]]>
